import turtle

wn = turtle.Screen()
wn.bgcolor("lightgreen")
gino = turtle.Turtle()
gino.shape("turtle")
gino.color("blue")
gino.pensize(3)
gino.speed(15)
gino.up()

for i in range(12) :
    gino.forward(100)
    gino.down()
    gino.forward(10)
    gino.up()
    gino.forward(20)
    gino.stamp()
    gino.backward(130)
    gino.left(30)

wn.exitonclick()
